One of my favourite little details in the new COLLINS website is this responsive border-radius.

--margin: calc((100% - var(--max-width)) / 2);
border-radius: clamp(1rem, calc(1.5rem - var(--margin)), 1.5rem);

https://t.co/mokwcgE2eM https://t.co/uJynwWNIYo

accordion transitions w/ css ::details-content, &lt;details&gt; + &lt;summary&gt; 🧑‍🍳

details:has(~ [open]) { --y: -1; }
[open] ~ details { --y: 1; }
details { translate: 0 calc(var(--y) * 1rem); }
[open]::details-content { height: fit-content; } https://t.co/WuVH4ifW1G

